rComments: He flip flops on what he wants from students. He'll tell you one thing from one meeting and then tell you to change everything the next. So inconsistent.

This man shows you that he is the nicest guy in this university but he forgets that you have to match your words with your actions. He is good with what he is doing from his childhood the gondola project and no one else is interested in that 5 Phd students, 100+ grad student and 1000+ undergrad student has worked on the same project. Please move on
He made lots of mistakes in class. The PPT is totally useless, and you have to attend each class for taking notes. Do more practices and you will be fine in final.

best prof ever, good looking to.
